stateMachineDiagram.name: State Machine Diagram - Passenger
stateMachineDiagram.description: This diagram shows the sequence of states for the class Passenger during its life in response to stimuli, together with its response and actions

state.name: Passenger waiting for the elevator
state.condition: p.boarded = false and p.served = false and p.inside = null

state.name: Passeger boarded in a elevator
state.condition: p.boarded = true and p.served = false and p.inside = e

state.name: Passenger served at his/her destin floor
state.condition: p.boarded = false and p.served = true and p.inside = null

stateMachineDiagram.name: State Machine Diagram - Elevator
stateMachineDiagram.description: This diagram shows the sequence of states for the class Elevator during its life in response to stimuli, together with its response and actions

state.name: Elevator with closed door stopped at a floor
state.condition: e.stopped = true and e.movingUp = false and e.movingDown = false and e.doorOpen = false

state.name: Elevator moving up
state.condition: e.stopped = false and e.movingUp = true and e.movingDown = false and e.doorOpen = false

state.name: Elevator moving down
state.condition: e.stopped = false and e.movingUp = false and e.movingDown = true and e.doorOpen = false

state.name: Elevator with open door stopped at a floor
state.condition: e.stopped = true and e.movingUp = false and e.movingDown = false and e.doorOpen = true

problem.name: Three Passengers 6 floors 1 elevator
problem.description: This problem has one building, three passenger to be served, six floors and a single elevator. The goal is serve all the passenger to their destin floor.
